column16: Miguel Sano grounds into a double play, shortstop Alcides Escobar to second baseman Whit Merrifield to first baseman Eric Hosmer.   Joe Mauer out at 2nd.
Robbie Grossman singles on a ground ball to center fielder Lorenzo Cain.
Jason Castro grounds out softly, second baseman Whit Merrifield to first baseman Eric Hosmer.
Roberto Perez grounds into a force out, fielded by third baseman Mike Moustakas.   Edwin Encarnacion out at 3rd.
Austin Jackson out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Lorenzo Cain.   Carlos Santana scores.
Jose Ramirez singles on a sharp line drive to right fielder Jorge Bonifacio.   Carlos Santana to 3rd.    Edwin Encarnacion to 2nd.
Edwin Encarnacion walks.   Carlos Santana to 2nd.
Carlos Santana singles on a ground ball to right fielder Jorge Bonifacio.   Bradley Zimmer scores.
Michael Brantley flies out to right fielder Jorge Bonifacio.   Bradley Zimmer to 3rd.
Bradley Zimmer doubles (2) on a line drive to right fielder Jorge Bonifacio, deflected by second baseman Whit Merrifield.   Jason Kipnis scores.
Jason Kipnis doubles (6) on a fly ball to center fielder Lorenzo Cain.
